A professional test automation framework for e-commerce applications built with Java, Selenium, TestNG, and Cucumber following industry best practices.

ğŸŒ Application Under Test
URL: https://www.saucedemo.com/

Credentials:

Username: standard_user

Password: secret_sauce

The Sauce Labs Demo site includes full e-commerce functionality with login, product browsing, cart management, and checkout - perfect for automation testing practice.

ğŸš€ Features
Page Object Model (POM) design pattern for maintainable code

Behavior-Driven Development (BDD) with Cucumber for business-readable tests

Data-Driven Testing with TestNG DataProvider

Automatic Screenshot Capture on test failures

Cross-Browser Testing support via WebDriverManager

Professional Reporting with TestNG and Cucumber HTML reports

